<p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#3333FF"><b><span style="font-size: 16.0pt; font-family: Arial">Clone MAC </span></b></font><font color="#3333FF"><b><span style="font-size: 16.0pt; font-family: Arial">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="javascript:print();"><img border="0" src="../image/Printer.gif" align="center" width="82" height="44"></a></span></b></font></p>
<table class="MsoNormalTable" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse: collapse; border: medium none">
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
    <b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Clonazione MAC</span></b></td> 
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left: medium none; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">L'indirizzo MAC del router è un codice univoco a 12 cifre che identifica un componente hardware. Alcuni ISP richiedono di registrare l'indirizzo MAC della scheda di rete, collegata al modem via cavo o DSL durante l'installazione. Se l'ISP richiede di registrare l'indirizzo MAC, è possibile individuarlo seguendo le istruzioni relative al sistema operativo del proprio PC.</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Per Windows 98 e Millennium:</span></p> 
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">1.<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Fare clic sul pulsante </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Start</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> e selezionare </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Esegui</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">.</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">2.<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Digitare </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">winipcfg</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> nel campo disponibile e premere </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">OK</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">.</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">3.<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Selezionare la scheda Ethernet in uso.</span></p> 
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">4.<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Fare clic su </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Ulteriori informazioni</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">.</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">5.<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Prendere nota dell'indirizzo MAC della scheda.</span></p> 
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Per Windows 2000 e XP:</span></p> 
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">1.<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Fare clic sul pulsante </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Start</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> e selezionare </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Esegui</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">.</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">2.<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Digitare </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">cmd</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> nel campo disponibile e premere </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">OK</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">.</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">3.<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Al prompt dei comandi, eseguire </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">ipconfig /all</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> e individuare l'indirizzo fisico della scheda.</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">4.<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Prendere nota dell'indirizzo MAC della scheda.</span></p> 
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Se si desidera clonare l'indirizzo MAC della scheda di rete sul router senza dover contattare l'ISP per modificare l'indirizzo MAC registrato, procedere come segue:</span></p> 
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">1.<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Selezionare </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Attiva</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">.</span></p> 
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">2.<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Immettere l'indirizzo MAC della scheda nel campo <i>Indirizzo MAC</i>.</span></p> 
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">3.<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Fare clic sul pulsante </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Salva impostazioni</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">.</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Per disattivare la clonazione dell'indirizzo MAC, mantenere l'impostazione predefinita </span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Disattiva</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">.</span></p>
